Comment: Here is yet another game from dave1973's mini-tournament! The interesting endgame here, as well as the wacky opening, makes this game well worth looking at!
This must be pretty rare. It is a passive, slow move that does absolutely nothing for White. If you're going to move that pawn, just play 2.c4, a much better opening for White - the Queen's Gambit.
